Kannegiesser Warns of Credit Crunch for German Firms, WAZ Says

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-09-30T03:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/kannegiesser-warns-of-credit-crunch-for-german-firms-waz-says.html
Martin Kannegiesser, head of the
Gesamtmetall lobby of engineering companies, said it is more
difficult for small and medium-sized German companies with weak
order books to borrow money from banks than during the last
financial crisis,  Westdeutsche Allgemeine Zeitung  reported,
citing an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  